{"id": 2671, "genre": 1001, "title": "今年最让你惦记的陌生人是谁？", "description": "一面之缘的路人、叫不出名字的快递小哥，或是公共事件里让人揪心的当事人，是谁让你不曾相识却真实地关心过？（题图来自：iStock ©️ nuvolanevicata）", "record_count": 1218, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181210172200vsDJ56LCyilNR4bq.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-12-13T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 316417, "content": "李成儒", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531168}, {"id": 316418, "content": "在秦皇陵遇到的古装小姐姐。惊鸿一面，难以忘怀。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1515881}, {"id": 316419, "content": "我有一次乘坐出租车，路上有个孕妇小姐姐打车，我让司机停下顺路拉上她，我下车之后她给我做了个笔芯的手势，现在的她应该小宝宝成功出生了吧❤️", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531182}, {"id": 316675, "content": "陈柏霖", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1152882}, {"id": 320517, "content": "张国荣", "image": "img/option/option/20190103142609h24eUiNjwAyO8cPJ.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1451963}, {"id": 316422, "content": "牛大伟~", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1508702}, {"id": 316423, "content": "熟悉的陌生人 牛大伟了呢~", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1508702}, {"id": 316424, "content": "马蓉", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1505842}, {"id": 316425, "content": "朱英菁", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1528211}, {"id": 316426, "content": "可能是我等了十八年的女朋友吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1412258}, {"id": 316427, "content": "刘雪瑶", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531236}, {"id": 316428, "content": "常年蹲点，路边同一坑位的，可怜兮兮的小乞丐，或是泄露天机的算命先生。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 574751}, {"id": 316429, "content": "还没见面的未来老公。", "image": "img/option/option/20181214081501zXCI9PKSb4p0oO2u.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1450393}, {"id": 316430, "content": "三军仪仗队的士兵们", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1358856}, {"id": 316431, "content": "相互对视一眼，并且点头打招呼的女孩", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531254}, {"id": 316432, "content": "失联了的姑且算是女朋友吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1530647}, {"id": 316688, "content": "那个撩了我一段时间然后消失了的篮球小奶狗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1429530}, {"id": 322320, "content": "Sophia", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1555754}, {"id": 316433, "content": "陈诺，一个心仪多年的女孩", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1394996}, {"id": 316435, "content": "冬天的小姐姐？还是走在大街上裹得紧紧的女生，安全感有木有", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531269}, {"id": 318995, "content": "许笑铭", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1499484}, {"id": 316948, "content": "宋某桥", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1532706}, {"id": 317205, "content": "卖烤冷面的阿姨和铁板烧的大叔", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1534999}, {"id": 316438, "content": "此时此刻，在此评论的her", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531273}, {"id": 316439, "content": "镇杰", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1223245}, {"id": 316951, "content": "今年让我最惦记的陌生人是谁呢？\n通讯录里的“他”算不算是陌生人呢？\n最熟悉的陌生人吧 现在也没必要惦记了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1532719}, {"id": 316440, "content": "陪我下山的那个男生", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198027}, {"id": 316441, "content": "梦伶图", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531279}, {"id": 317466, "content": "火车站帮拎箱子的小哥哥", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1535982}, {"id": 316443, "content": "陪我爬陡峰的人 哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1525250}, {"id": 316699, "content": "每一个打过照面彼此表达过善意的陌生人吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1496866}, {"id": 316955, "content": "宋思睿", "image": "img/option/option/20181215211557dzhyVbfaorUC1cuE", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1532743}, {"id": 327964, "content": "骄阳", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1584294}, {"id": 316444, "content": "有一天在小区路上遇见的摆摊母女。那是本次寒潮到来的降温之夜，路过听见小姑娘在吵着要吃面包，就去给她买了一个小的蒸蛋糕。天气还是很冷，不知道她们在哪里摆摊，希望她们一切都好。别的素未谋面的小贩们也一样。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1074638}, {"id": 316445, "content": "那些有勇气发声，但被消失的人！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1087449}, {"id": 318493, "content": "有一天帮一个外国客人打印，因为不太熟练，客人很耐心的鼓励我，刚刚实习的我真的很感激她虽然我们交流都不是很顺畅，结果走的时候她表情有些失落的和我说my father died today.我只是拍了拍她的肩膀说sorry，但是我应该去抱抱她的，她看上去那么难过。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1540089}, {"id": 316447, "content": "支教回来之后也许再也没办法见到的小朋友们", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1530285}, {"id": 316448, "content": "xzq", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531321}, {"id": 316449, "content": "是我心里一直很喜欢很挂念的一个男人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1470553}, {"id": 318241, "content": "被家暴的小男孩", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1399545}, {"id": 316451, "content": "那个人是梦想吧，也叫年轻人的迷茫", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531334}, {"id": 319779, "content": "温格", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1417997}, {"id": 316452, "content": "我的彩虹小马", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1020509}, {"id": 316964, "content": "没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1451953}, {"id": 316453, "content": "在我刚搬家次日从我家楼上21层跳楼到楼门口自杀成功的邻居", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 280023}, {"id": 316966, "content": "我们游戏的盟主，因为他已经离线六天了，后天他再不上线盟主就换人了。。。。好奇他的死活", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1529171}, {"id": 318502, "content": "双十一因为送不完货怕被投诉的人呆呆的送货员大叔。\n挺担心他被解雇，刚刚又给我打电话告诉我快递到了，还好还好😄", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 444860}, {"id": 316969, "content": "保护了我免受中年大叔骚扰的星巴克店员小哥", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1519605}, {"id": 316458, "content": "金庸先生", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1528501}, {"id": 317226, "content": "虵", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1532869}]}